descr: "A request to supply a diet, formula feeding (enteral) or oral nutritional supplement to a patient/resident."

fields.name: schedule
fields.descr: "The time period and frequency at which the enteral formula should be delivered to the patient."

fields.name: quantity
fields.descr: "The volume of formula to provide to the patient per the specified administration schedule."

fields.name: rateSimpleQuantity
fields.descr: "The rate of administration of formula via a feeding pump, e.g. 60 mL per hour, according to the specified schedule."

fields.name: rateRatio
fields.descr: "The rate of administration of formula via a feeding pump, e.g. 60 mL per hour, according to the specified schedule."
